```plantuml
@startuml GoogleCloudPlatform_gke-pubsub-websocket-adapter

actor Client
participant "websocketd" as WebSocketD
participant "pulltop" as PullTop
participant "Google Cloud Pub/Sub" as PubSub

Client -> WebSocketD: Connect to WebSocket
WebSocketD -> PullTop: Request for latest messages
PullTop -> PubSub: Pull messages from the subscribed topic
PubSub -> PullTop: Return messages
PullTop -> WebSocketD: Forward messages
WebSocketD -> Client: Push messages to client

note right of WebSocketD
  WebSocketD stores messages 
  temporarily in ephemeral storage
end note

Client -> WebSocketD: Disconnect
WebSocketD -> Client: Acknowledge disconnect

@enduml
```